name: The Cryptic Sphere, Animated Trading Card No. 4
description: This is the animated trading card no. 4 of the Cryptic Sphere with a cryptic amount of 100. The cryptic amount is either 10, 20, 50, 100, 200, or 500, so six related trading cards make up a set. The Cryptic Sphere is a 3D graphic experiment by The Vectorizer. It is a play of changing shapes, lights, colors and surfaces. Each Cryptic Sphere is created individually by hand with great effort. There are recurring elements but no automated generation processes.
